# Script Manager Configuration Example

# Database Configuration
# Path to SQLite database file
# DATABASE_PATH=./data/scripts.db

# API Configuration
# Port for the backend API server
# API_PORT=8000

# Scanning Configuration
# Maximum file size to index in bytes (default: 10MB)
# MAX_FILE_SIZE=10485760

# CORS Configuration
# Allowed origins for CORS (comma-separated)
# ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:5173

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env in the backend directory
# 2. Uncomment and modify the values you want to change
# 3. Restart the backend server for changes to take effect
